			"description": "### üë§ **User Folder Overview**\n\nThis folder handles all user-related operations including:\n\n- ‚úÖ **Registration** (`/user/create`) ‚Äî Users and agents can register with email, phoneNo, password, name, nidno, address. A wallet is created automatically with a default balance of TK50.\n    \n- ‚úÖ **Get My Info** (`/user/me`) ‚Äî Authenticated users can retrieve their profile.\n    \n- ‚úÖ **Password Change** (`/user/update-password`) ‚Äî Allows users to update passwords securely.\n    \n- ‚úÖ **Admin Controls**:\n    \n    - Get all/one users\n        \n    - Update user by ID (role/status/verification)\n        \n    - Delete user\n        \n- ‚úÖ **Role Support**: Admin, User, and Agent"
